Installation Instructions
=========================

DirectFB-examples is built using Meson.

First, configure the build:

  $ meson setup build/

Linux
=====

On Linux, start the build with:

  $ meson compile -C build/

And install DirectFB-examples using:

  $ meson install -C build/

NuttX
=====

On NuttX, copy the DirectFB-examples directory to your NuttX apps/examples/ directory.
